Dracula: Pages From a Virgin's Diary;;73;;87;;NC;;In this ballet version of Bram Stoker's classic vampire tale, Dracula (Zhang Wei-Qiang) arrives in London and performs a dance of seduction with the virgin Lucy (Tara Birtwhistle), whom he turns into a ravenous monster. Lucy's three suitors vow revenge even as Dracula stalks his next victim. When the trio's efforts prove counterproductive, professional vampire hunter Van Helsing (David Moroni) enters the picture and meets Dracula in a climactic battle.;;Horror;;Guy Maddin;;2002;;Zhang Wei-Qiang,David Moroni,Tara Birtwhistle,Stephane Leonard,Keir Knight;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dracula_pages_from_a_virgins_diary